# Privacy Policy for Decide For Me - Stop Thinking

**Last Updated: February 23, 2026**

## Overview

Decide For Me - Stop Thinking ("the App") is developed by Mert Can Cibuk. This privacy policy explains how we handle your information.

## Data Collection

### Advertising Data
The free version of the App displays advertisements through Google AdMob. AdMob may collect:
- Device advertising identifier (IDFA/GAID)
- General location data (country/region level)
- Device information (model, OS version)
- Ad interaction data

This data is collected by Google and is governed by Google's Privacy Policy: https://policies.google.com/privacy

### Pro Users
Users who purchase the Pro upgrade will not see any advertisements, and no advertising-related data will be collected.

### App Data
The App stores your decision history locally on your device. This data:
- Never leaves your device
- Is not transmitted to any server
- Is not accessible to us or any third party
- Can be deleted by uninstalling the App

## Third-Party Services

| Service | Purpose | Privacy Policy |
|---------|---------|----------------|
| Google AdMob | Advertising (free version only) | https://policies.google.com/privacy |

## Children's Privacy

The App is not directed to children under 13. AdMob is configured to comply with COPPA regulations.

## Your Choices

- **Opt out of personalized ads**: Use your device's "Limit Ad Tracking" or "Opt out of Ads Personalization" setting
- **Remove all ads**: Purchase the Pro upgrade within the app

## Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.

